21 August 2012Members of the media are invited to the Inter-Ministerial Committee (IMC) on Marikana Tragedy meeting with the South African Council of Churches(SACC) at the Rustenburg Civic Centre. The IMC will also meet with traditional leaders. There will be a joint media briefings after the meeting. Date: 21 August 2012 (Tuesday) Time: 11:00 Venue: Rustenburg Civic Centre, Rustenburg Enquiries: Harold Maloka Cell: 082 847 9799 or maloka.harold@gmail.comIssued by the Inter-Ministerial Committee